WEBVTT

00:11:57.197 --> 00:12:01.390
or perhaps even in a greenhouse on Mars.

00:12:02.025 --> 00:12:05.520
I know it sounds crazy,
but think about this:

00:12:05.544 --> 00:12:07.377
a new Provincetown,

00:12:07.401 --> 00:12:09.043
a new hometown,

00:12:09.067 --> 00:12:12.545
a place that might be familiar
that's also good for pollinators

00:12:12.569 --> 00:12:13.933
for a stable food system,

00:12:13.957 --> 00:12:16.008
when we're thinking about the future.

00:12:17.230 --> 00:12:20.522
Now, together, we know
what's saving bees --

00:12:20.546 --> 00:12:22.284
by planting diverse habitat.

00:12:22.741 --> 00:12:26.856
Now, together, we know how bees
are going to save us --

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:30.061
by being barometers
for environmental health,